Class Doctor

public class Doctor extends User
Represents a doctor user in the patient portal system. Inherits common user properties and methods from the User class.

      public Doctor(int account_number, String username, String email_address, String role, String name, String password)
      Constructs a new Patient object with the specified account details.
      Parameters:
      account_number - the unique account number for the patient
      username - the username used for patient login
      email_address - the patient's email address
      role - the role assigned to this user (typically "doctor")
      name - the full name of the patient
      password - the patient's account password
